title: LF Chill Guys & Girls
body:
Im a b5 scrub looking for people who wouldnt mind ranking up together?
Im on whenever I can be. 
Jgl/Supp main but can go anywhere.
IGN: Kandikanin

replies.body: If your looking for people you should check us out at https://ethereal-gaming.com/ were a positive gaming community playing norms and ranked.
My thing is jg or top but mainly jg

I probably play at bronze 5 skill level. I prefer Top, Adc, Mid in that order. I can't jungle and don't like support. I am more passive and play for late game. I am probably not the best in team fights. I have always solo Queue but am tired of auto fill and getting so many bad players so I would like to find a team to play with. I play around 5:00 am to 9:00 am eastern time.
